      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good condition and has been lovingly maintained, ensuring it's ready for many more miles of memories. While you might notice some minor cosmetic wear from its previous adventures, its performance and overall appeal remain strong. It's a reliable, stylish choice for anyone looking for a high-quality ride at a great value!",
