    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of unparalleled caliber, maintained to a fastidious standard that mirrors its original showroom delivery. This specimen exhibits pristine exterior surfaces and an interior devoid of wear, representing the pinnacle of its class. Mechanically flawless and historically preserved, it offers a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection. We invite rigorous inspection to confirm its superlative status.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
